1.title: Swapping EqualTo
1.text: Double click on '=' to swap both sides of equations

1.title: Adding two numbers
1.text: Double click on '+' to add the two numbers

1.title: Adding three numbers
1.text: Drag and smoosh to add the numbers

2.title: Swapping expression
2.text: Click and drag '+' to the left side

3.title: Factoring
3.text: Move one 'x' on top of another 'x' to factor

3.title: Distribution
3.text: Move the x into the sum to distribute
